Banglore
Experience elegance and luxury at its finest with our premium W jaalis in the stunning St. Marks Hotel, Bangalore. Our exquisite craftsmanship adds a touch of natural exoticism, the ambiance to new heights. Discover the beauty of sophistication.
[CommercialSuperdryBangloreIn Bangalore&#8217;s vibrant Mall of Asia, Urbanclay&#8217;s craftsmanship shines through in the brick cladding work at Superdry&#8217;s flagship store. The brick cladding, urbanclay, adds a touch of modernity while paying homage to the city&#8217;s architectural heritage. Each brick is meticulously crafted, reflecting Urbanclay&#8217;s commitment to quality and innovation. As Bangalore evolves, so does Urbanclay, blending tradition with contemporary design to create spaces that are both timeless and stylish.View Project →](https://claytile.in/projects/superdry-bangalore)

### Superdry
Banglore
In Bangalore&#8217;s vibrant Mall of Asia, Urbanclay&#8217;s craftsmanship shines through in the brick cladding work at Superdry&#8217;s flagship store. The brick cladding, urbanclay, adds a touch of modernity while paying homage to the city&#8217;s architectural heritage. Each brick is meticulously crafted, reflecting Urbanclay&#8217;s commitment to quality and innovation. As Bangalore evolves, so does Urbanclay, blending tradition with contemporary design to create spaces that are both timeless and stylish.
[Bhairavi Residence AurangabadThe Bhairavi residence in Aurangabad is deeply rooted in spirituality whilst embracing modern aesthetics, which is Golden Kalda Design Studio&#8217;s inherit idea.&nbsp;Hand crafted clay brick tiles with a dramatic terracotta red body bears a lasting imprint on mind that reminds the comfort of earthy warmth of old Indian homes.&nbsp;Therefore, harmony of this material pallet with stylish, modern organizing and light modern archetype is achieved.&nbsp;The space convey a soothing and contemplative environment by means of using natural materials in decor and the absence of strangle and constricting architectural components.&nbsp;By skillfully implementing the Grecian antiquity and the modern-day leading design trends, the interior of the place reflects a perfect harmony – a heaven to be contended with, characterized by both the physical and the spiritual well-being of its inhabitants.View Project →](https://claytile.in/projects/bhairavi-residence-aurangabad)

### Bhairavi Residence
Aurangabad
The Bhairavi residence in Aurangabad is deeply rooted in spirituality whilst embracing modern aesthetics, which is Golden Kalda Design Studio&#8217;s inherit idea.&nbsp;Hand crafted clay brick tiles with a dramatic terracotta red body bears a lasting imprint on mind that reminds the comfort of earthy warmth of old Indian homes.&nbsp;Therefore, harmony of this material pallet with stylish, modern organizing and light modern archetype is achieved.&nbsp;The space convey a soothing and contemplative environment by means of using natural materials in decor and the absence of strangle and constricting architectural components.&nbsp;By skillfully implementing the Grecian antiquity and the modern-day leading design trends, the interior of the place reflects a perfect harmony – a heaven to be contended with, characterized by both the physical and the spiritual well-being of its inhabitants.
[View All Projects→](https://claytile.in/projects)

